              "width": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "vEAP8",
                  "fill": "#94A3B8",
                  "content": "ABOUT",
                  "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                  "fontSize": 11,
                  "fontWeight": "normal",
                  "letterSpacing": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "wFLwx",
                  "name": "hH1",
                  "fill": {
                    "type": "gradient",
                    "gradientType": "linear",
                    "enabled": true,
                    "rotation": 90,
                    "size": {
                      "height": 1
                    },
                    "colors": [
                      {
                        "color": "#0F62FE",
                        "position": 0
                      },
                      {
                        "color": "#0043CE",
                        "position": 1
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fit_content(565)",
                  "content": "The Science of Thinking, Reimagined.",
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 48,
                  "fontWeight": "600"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "7B7xg",
                  "fill": "#64748B",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Aanvikshiki is rooted in the ancient Indian discipline of inquiry and reasoning — Ānvīkṣikī, the science of critical thinking — reinterpreted for modern organizations navigating complexity, uncertainty, and technological change.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "E64xX",
              "name": "ahdrRight",
              "metadata": {
                "type": "unsplash",
                "username": "silverkblack",
                "link": "https://unsplash.com/@silverkblack",
                "author": "Vitaly Gariev"
              },
              "width": 560,
              "height": 420,
              "fill": {
                "type": "image",
                "enabled": true,
                "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1758876019274-b5b3a459b1cf?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w4NDM0ODN8MHwxfHJhbmRvbXx8fHx8fHx8fDE3NzQ3ODM0NDR8&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080",
                "mode": "fill"
              },
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#E2E8F0"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "Rjqbr",
          "name": "etym",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "#F8FAFC",
          "stroke": {
            "thickness": {
              "bottom": 1
            },
            "fill": "#E2E8F0"
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 20,
          "padding": [
            80,
            60
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "AgoIk",
              "fill": "#94A3B8",
              "content": "THE NAME",
              "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
              "fontSize": 11,
              "fontWeight": "normal",
              "letterSpacing": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "GBq6Q",
              "fill": "#0f172a",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 680,
              "content": "Ancient Wisdom. Modern Execution.",
              "lineHeight": 1.25,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 24,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "dyqxr",
              "fill": "#64748B",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 680,
              "content": "Ānvīkṣikī appears in the Arthashastra — Kautilya's treatise on statecraft — as one of the four sciences a leader must master. It is defined as the lamp of all learning, the means of all action, and the foundation of all knowledge.",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "qbK5M",
              "fill": "#64748B",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 680,
              "content": "We took the name because it captures what we believe is missing in most AI-enabled organizations: not more data, not more models, but a rigorous discipline of inquiry that precedes any of it. The ancient idea is that structured thinking is not a soft skill — it is a strategic capability. That belief is the foundation of everything we do.",
              "lineHeight": 1.7,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "o6HDe",
          "name": "beliefSec",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "stroke": {
            "thickness": {
              "bottom": 1
            },
            "fill": "#E2E8F0"
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 48,
          "padding": [
            80,
            60
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "2u9bz",
              "fill": "#94A3B8",
              "content": "WHAT WE BELIEVE",
              "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
              "fontSize": 11,
              "fontWeight": "normal",
              "letterSpacing": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "LCne3",
              "name": "bList",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "iFicT",
                  "name": "b1",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 40,
                  "padding": [
                    32,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "jjdJb",
                      "fill": "#0f172a",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 400,
                      "content": "Clarity beats speed.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.3,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "BtFCg",
                      "fill": "#64748B",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Most organizations move fast in the wrong direction. We slow the thinking down before the execution speeds up.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "xaCR3",
                  "name": "b2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "stroke": {
                    "thickness": {
                      "top": 1
                    },
                    "fill": "#E2E8F0"
                  },
                  "gap": 40,
                  "padding": [
                    32,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "67AjP",
                      "fill": "#0f172a",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 400,
                      "content": "Thinking beats reacting.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.3,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "GgOuX",
                      "fill": "#64748B",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Reactive organizations mistake activity for progress. Structured thinking creates the conditions for decisions that hold under pressure.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "fSACG",
                  "name": "b3",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "stroke": {
                    "thickness": {
                      "top": 1
                    },
                    "fill": "#E2E8F0"
                  },
                  "gap": 40,
                  "padding": [
                    32,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "5GOtU",
                      "fill": "#0f172a",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 400,
                      "content": "Ethics beats short-term gains.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.3,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "UpfyB",
                      "fill": "#64748B",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Intelligence without integrity compounds risk. Every framework we build embeds the question: what are the downstream consequences of this decision?",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "t1INW",
          "name": "princSec",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "stroke": {
            "thickness": {
              "bottom": 1
            },
            "fill": "#E2E8F0"
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 48,
          "padding": [
            80,
            60
          ],
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "cwlBT",
              "fill": "#94A3B8",
              "content": "HOW WE OPERATE",
              "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
              "fontSize": 11,
              "fontWeight": "normal",
              "letterSpacing": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "TjcxD",
              "name": "pList",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "BW0b9",
                  "name": "p1",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "gap": 24,
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "cmafY",
                      "fill": "#94A3B8",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 32,
                      "content": "01",
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 11,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "IpblT",
                      "fill": "#0f172a",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 260,
                      "content": "Inquiry before conclusion",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "WX6oA",
                      "fill": "#64748B",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "We do not arrive at engagements with pre-formed answers. We arrive with structured questions. The problem defines the approach — not the other way around.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.65,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "lWQ3B",
                  "name": "p2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "stroke": {
                    "thickness": {
                      "top": 1
                    },
                    "fill": "#E2E8F0"
                  },
                  "gap": 24,
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "axCyG",
                      "fill": "#94A3B8",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 32,
                      "content": "02",
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 11,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "shW2d",
                      "fill": "#0f172a",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 260,
                      "content": "Transparency over comfort",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "bNpmr",
                      "fill": "#64748B",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "We tell clients what we find, not what they want to hear. A strategic assessment that obscures inconvenient truths is not an assessment — it is a performance.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.65,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "2sAjF",
                  "name": "p3",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "stroke": {
                    "thickness": {
                      "top": 1
                    },
                    "fill": "#E2E8F0"
                  },
                  "gap": 24,
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Vsbwp",
                      "fill": "#94A3B8",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 32,
                      "content": "03",
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 11,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "noP14",
                      "fill": "#0f172a",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 260,
                      "content": "Human judgment, amplified",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "jI84d",
                      "fill": "#64748B",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "AI is the instrument. Human judgment remains the authority. We design systems that sharpen decision-making rather than replace it.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.65,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "XPgae",
                  "name": "p4",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "stroke": {
                    "thickness": {
                      "top": 1
                    },
                    "fill": "#E2E8F0"
                  },
                  "gap": 24,
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "PM0aV",
                      "fill": "#94A3B8",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 32,
                      "content": "04",
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 11,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "xdxuI",
                      "fill": "#0f172a",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 260,
                      "content": "Long arc thinking",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "DTNLo",
                      "fill": "#64748B",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "The decisions that matter most play out over years, not quarters. We build frameworks that remain sound under conditions that don't yet exist.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.65,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
