                  "fill": "#64748B",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Infrastructure analysis was completed in 4 days. The output was not a report — it was a migration architecture derived directly from the dependency graph topology. The organization entered its migration with complete strategic clarity about what it had, what depended on what, and in what order to move it.",
